item.title: Swedish teen and Ethiopian Prime Minister .. Which is the most likely to win the Nobel Peace Prize?
item.description: Swedish teenager Greta Thunberg tops the list of favorites to win the Nobel Peace Prize in 2019, while others rule out her crowning under the nomination of Ethiopian Prime Minister Abe Ahmed and important international organizations.
